title: Person Medium Dark Skin Tone White Hair
alsoKnownAs: White Haired Person Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: A person with white hair and a medium-dark skin tone. Typically used to signify an elder, someone with wisdom, or a distinguished person.
apple_vendor_description: The person with medium-dark skin tone and white hair emoji on Apple devices is a dignified representation, featuring gentle gradients and realistic lighting that highlight their distinguished look. The soft, rounded edges of their form convey a sense of wisdom and experience. This emoji is often used to represent an elder, a mentor, or someone possessing significant knowledge and maturity.
